        "Dear Sagar,",
        "I am writing this letter to apologize to you for not paying your money back on time, which I have taken on June 4th the due date was July 4th  and the amount was $2000. I have taken that money for my course as you know I am taking music classes which will help my career.",
        "Firstly, I planned to give you cash on time but unfortunately, I lost my job because of covid as I work in the restaurant it was closed for 4 weeks due to government regulations. Moreover, it was very hard to survive somehow I tried to make money with my music classes which were enough for my room rent and grocery.",
